content:
Available in: Lightning Experience. Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Einstein Reply Recommendations is included in the Einstein for Service add-on license.

To build the Einstein Reply Recommendations model:

Customize Application

From Setup, enter Einstein Reply Recommendations.
Click Let’s Go.
If you don’t have enough closed chats to build a model, get a message here.
Click Build Model.

Einstein creates two models from this initial build. One identifies potential reply templates and a second identifies data patterns in live chats and recommends that reply to agents in real time.

After the initial build, each month Einstein retrains the model that recommends replies to your agents in real time. To see your last build date, select Model Setup.

Enable Einstein Reply Recommendations

Review and Publish Replies
title: Building Einstein Reply Recommendation Models
